					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">My much bigger gripe was how difficult it would be to fit everything in vram on the SNES, which is why I devised my idea of having every sprite have its own slot and identical sprites using the same slot for basically perfect space usage. However, you don't even have to deal with this on the NES.</div>

